&nbsp;
The county sheriff admitted that there is fear that the girl may have taken her life, even if the suitcase hypothesis leaves some hope. But with the passing of days, the situation gets more worrying. Investigators have, however, excluded the possibility of kidnapping with the aim of asking for a ransom to parents. A friend of the girl told she had seen Mint north of San Francisco, but she wouldn't provide any more useful details.
