&nbsp;
In 2018 the then Governor of New York Andrew Cuomo was forced to declare the state of emergency after a video had shown a snake moving along a handrail and then crouching at the end of a car. The passenger who had shot the pictures, told me that the reptile owner had kissed the snake and then let him move along the train.
